snippet: A radio station funded by the American government says its office in Baku, the capital, has been raided by prosecutors who claim to have a court decision to shut it down....

headline.print_headline: Azerbaijan: Prosecutors Raid Radio Station Funded by U.S.
headline.main: Azerbaijan: Prosecutors Raid Radio Station Funded by U.S.

lead_paragraph: A radio station funded by the American government says its office in Baku, the capital, has been raided by prosecutors who claim to have a court decision to shut it down.
